      "source": [
        "![](images/paste-46.png)\n",
        "\n",
        "-   Usando el rango intercuartil\n",
        "\n",
        "    -   Rango intercuartil (IQR)\n",
        "\n",
        "        -   IQR = 75th - 25th percentil\n",
        "\n",
        "        -   Upper outliers \\> 75th percentile + (1.5 \\* IQR)\n",
        "\n",
